    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1、 情緒領域之介紹：情緒在生活與社會互動中的重要性。<br>2、 情緒的理論基礎。<br>3、 情緒能力：覺察與辨識、表達、理解與調節。<br>4、 增進幼兒的信任、自主及自發之基本態度。<br>5、 以遊戲及創造性材料協助幼兒發展情緒能力。",
        "en": "1.Introduction to the Emotional Domain: The importance of emotions in life and social interaction.<br>2. The theoretical basis of emotion.<br>3. Emotional ability: awareness and identification, expression, understanding and regulation.<br>4. Improve children's basic attitude of trust, autonomy and spontaneity.<br>5. Use games and creative materials to help children develop emotional abilities."
